Package ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.profile

Class Profile

java.lang.Object
ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.database.DocumentSerializable
ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.profile.Profile
public class Profile extends DocumentSerializable
This class represents a user profile. Include information about the name, homepage, contact info, notifications and any events hosted or joined.
